Delhi
Aug 29, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Molestation
Description:
			The incident took place in Central Delhi's Patel Nagar area where a four-year-old girl was allegedly molested by four juvenile who were playing with her yesterday.

The juvenile, who lived in the nearby area, allegedly touched the girl inappropriately while playing with her.

The incident came to light when the victim narrated her ordeal to her mother, who later reported the incident to the police.

The boys who are in the age group from 9-13 years were all apprehended by the police. 

Source: Press Trust of India